 961, \"to\": 978}, {\"ngram\": \"the proper perspective\", \"from\": 1043, \"to\": 1065}, {\"ngram\": \"an uplifting tournament\", \"from\": 1072, \"to\": 1095}, {\"ngram\": \"Le Golf National\", \"from\": 1099, \"to\": 1115}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cAmazing.\", \"from\": 1119, \"to\": 1130, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"We were talking about it out there and Nico (Nicolai Hojgaard) reckons it's the best tournament he's ever been involved in, and he's played a Ryder Cup,\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d McIlroy said after finishing tied for fifth, his shot at a medal drowned by a wedge shot that came up short on the 15th\\u00c2 hole.\", \"from\": 1131, \"to\": 1413, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1176, \"end\": 1183, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Saint_Nicholas\", \"score\": 0.9999999991646291, \"rank\": 8.353986009415105e-10, \"text\": \"Nicolai\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Saint_Nicholas\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Saint_Nicholas\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Nico\", \"from\": 1170, \"to\": 1174}, {\"ngram\": \"the best tournament\", \"from\": 1207, \"to\": 1226}, {\"ngram\": \"a Ryder Cup\", \"from\": 1271, \"to\": 1282}, {\"ngram\": \"McIlroy\", \"from\": 1287, \"to\": 1294}, {\"ngram\": \"a medal\", \"from\": 1344, \"to\": 1351}, {\"ngram\": \"a wedge shot\", \"from\": 1363, \"to\": 1375}, {\"ngram\": \"the 15th\\u00c2 hole\", \"from\": 1398, \"to\": 1412}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cI still think that the Ryder Cup is the best tournament that we have in our game, pure competition, and I think this has the potential to be right up there with it.\", \"from\": 1415, \"to\": 1582, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cI\", \"from\": 1415, \"to\": 1419}, {\"ngram\": \"the Ryder Cup\", \"from\": 1437, \"to\": 1450}, {\"ngram\": \"the best tournament\", \"from\": 1454, \"to\": 1473}, {\"ngram\": \"our game\", \"from\": 1490, \"to\": 1498}, {\"ngram\": \"pure competition\", \"from\": 1500, \"to\": 1516}, {\"ngram\": \"the potential\", \"from\": 1539, \"to\": 1552}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I think with how much of a sh-tshow the game of golf is right now and you think about the two tournaments that might be the purest form of competition in our sport, we do not play for money in it.\", \"from\": 1583, \"to\": 1779, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a sh-tshow\", \"from\": 1608, \"to\": 1618}, {\"ngram\": \"the game\", \"from\": 1619, \"to\": 1627}, {\"ngram\": \"golf\", \"from\": 1631, \"to\": 1635}, {\"ngram\": \"the two tournaments\", \"from\": 1669, \"to\": 1688}, {\"ngram\": \"the purest form\", \"from\": 1703, \"to\": 1718}, {\"ngram\": \"competition\", \"from\": 1722, \"to\": 1733}, {\"ngram\": \"our sport\", \"from\": 1737, \"to\": 1746}, {\"ngram\": \"money\", \"from\": 1767, \"to\": 1772}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cSo it speaks volumes for what's important in sports and what's important, I think every single player this week has had an amazing experience.\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d McIlroy, of course, was referencing the rift in the game that has existed for two years since the launch of the LIV Golf League and several prominent players bolting for big paydays and a new format.\", \"from\": 1781, \"to\": 2130, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2043, \"end\": 2051, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/LIV_Golf\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"LIV Golf\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/LIV_Golf\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/LIV_Golf\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"volumes\", \"from\": 1797, \"to\": 1804}, {\"ngram\": \"sports\", \"from\": 1829, \"to\": 1835}, {\"ngram\": \"every single player\", \"from\": 1866, \"to\": 1885}, {\"ngram\": \"an amazing experience.\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d McIlroy\", \"from\": 1904, \"to\": 1937}, {\"ngram\": \"course\", \"from\": 1942, \"to\": 1948}, {\"ngram\": \"the rift\", \"from\": 1966, \"to\": 1974}, {\"ngram\": \"the game\", \"from\": 1978, \"to\": 1986}, {\"ngram\": \"two years\", \"from\": 2008, \"to\": 2017}, {\"ngram\": \"the launch\", \"from\": 2024, \"to\": 2034}, {\"ngram\": \"several prominent players\", \"from\": 2062, \"to\": 2087}, {\"ngram\": \"big paydays\", \"from\": 2100, \"to\": 2111}, {\"ngram\": \"a new format\", \"from\": 2116, \"to\": 2128}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Since then, the two sides have attempted to come to some agreement, without a resolution to date.\", \"from\": 2132, \"to\": 2229, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the two sides\", \"from\": 2144, \"to\": 2157}, {\"ngram\": \"some agreement\", \"from\": 2184, \"to\": 2198}, {\"ngram\": \"a resolution\", \"from\": 2208, \"to\": 2220}, {\"ngram\": \"date\", \"from\": 2224, \"to\": 2228}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But this week, it was about the golf.\", \"from\": 2231, \"to\": 2268, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the golf\", \"from\": 2259, \"to\": 2267}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Rahm, who tied for fifth, was a golfer and his association with LIV Golf was not a huge talking point.\", \"from\": 2269, \"to\": 2371, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2333, \"end\": 2341, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/LIV_Golf\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"LIV Golf\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/LIV_Golf\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/LIV_Golf\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Rahm\", \"from\": 2269, \"to\": 2273}, {\"ngram\": \"fifth\", \"from\": 2288, \"to\": 2293}, {\"ngram\": \"a golfer\", \"from\": 2299, \"to\": 2307}, {\"ngram\": \"his association\", \"from\": 2312, \"to\": 2327}, {\"ngram\": \"a huge talking point\", \"from\": 2350, \"to\": 2370}]}, {\"sentence\": \"There were no questions about the Public Investment Fund or the negotiations with the Strategic Sports Group or any of the issues that are dogging the game.\", \"from\": 2372, \"to\": 2528, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2406, \"end\": 2428, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Public_Investment_Fund\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Public Investment Fund\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Public_Investment_Fund\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Public_Investment_Fund\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"no questions\", \"from\": 2383, \"to\": 2395}, {\"ngram\": \"the negotiations\", \"from\": 2432, \"to\": 2448}, {\"ngram\": \"the Strategic Sports Group\", \"from\": 2454, \"to\": 2480}, {\"ngram\": \"the issues\", \"from\": 2491, \"to\": 2501}, {\"ngram\": \"the game\", \"from\": 2519, \"to\": 2527}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Instead, it was golf on a grand stage with players once skeptical about the entire Olympic golf experience who were loving it.\", \"from\": 2530, \"to\": 2656, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"golf\", \"from\": 2546, \"to\": 2550}, {\"ngram\": \"a grand stage\", \"from\": 2554, \"to\": 2567}, {\"ngram\": \"players\", \"from\": 2573, \"to\": 2580}, {\"ngram\": \"the entire Olympic golf experience\", \"from\": 2602, \"to\": 2636}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cIt\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s amazing what sport can do to bring people together,\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d said Australia\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s Jason Day, who tied for ninth, having skipped the 2016 Olympics when he was ranked No.\", \"from\": 2658, \"to\": 2828, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"what sport\", \"from\": 2676, \"to\": 2686}, {\"ngram\": \"people\", \"from\": 2703, \"to\": 2709}, {\"ngram\": \"\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d\", \"from\": 2719, \"to\": 2722}, {\"ngram\": \"Jason Day\", \"from\": 2742, \"to\": 2751}, {\"ngram\": \"the 2016 Olympics\", \"from\": 2788, \"to\": 2805}]}, {\"sentence\": \"1 in the world.\", \"from\": 2829, \"to\": 2844, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the world\", \"from\": 2834, \"to\": 2843}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cThis is a week that we are not playing for money.\", \"from\": 2845, \"to\": 2897, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cThis\", \"from\": 2845, \"to\": 2852}, {\"ngram\": \"a week\", \"from\": 2856, \"to\": 2862}, {\"ngram\": \"money\", \"from\": 2891, \"to\": 2896}]}, {\"sentence\": \"We are playing for a medal and your country.\", \"from\": 2898, \"to\": 2942, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a medal\", \"from\": 2917, \"to\": 2924}, {\"ngram\": \"your country\", \"from\": 2929, \"to\": 2941}]}, {\"sentence\": \"You are weighing it on your chest and it's brought out old feelings that I thought I did not have and I still have deep down and why we play golf and why we love it so much.\", \"from\": 2943, \"to\": 3116, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"your chest\", \"from\": 2966, \"to\": 2976}, {\"ngram\": \"old feelings\", \"from\": 2998, \"to\": 3010}, {\"ngram\": \"golf\", \"from\": 3084, \"to\": 3088}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cSo it was impressive to see all the different countries out there.\", \"from\": 3118, \"to\": 3187, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"all the different countries\", \"from\": 3149, \"to\": 3176}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I thoroughly enjoyed the week and I am hoping that I get to play L.A. in four years.\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d The final round began with seven of the top 15 golfers in the Official World Golf Ranking in the top 10: Scheffler, Xander Schauffele, McIlroy, Rahm, Fleetwood, Matsuyama, Ludvig Aberg and Tom Kim.\", \"from\": 3188, \"to\": 3474, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3253, \"end\": 3257, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Los_Angeles\", \"score\": 0.9999973517918583, \"rank\": 2.6460417538389737e-06, \"text\": \"L.A.\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Los_Angeles\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Los_Angeles\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"four years.\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d\", \"from\": 3261, \"to\": 3275}, {\"ngram\": \"The final round\", \"from\": 3276, \"to\": 3291}, {\"ngram\": \"the top 15 golfers\", \"from\": 3312, \"to\": 3330}, {\"ngram\": \"the Official World Golf Ranking\", \"from\": 3334, \"to\": 3365}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Throw in Day, Hojgaard, Joaquin Niemann and Perez on the outskirts of medal contention, and you could not ask for a better stage to showcase the game.\", \"from\": 3476, \"to\": 3626, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3500, \"end\": 3507, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Joaquin_Phoenix\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.1260629017506359e-20, \"text\": \"Joaquin\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Joaquin_Phoenix\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Joaquin_Phoenix\"}, {\"begin\": 3508, \"end\": 3515, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jeff_Niemann\", \"score\": 0.9999189133649117, \"rank\": 8.108419889100158e-05, \"text\": \"Niemann\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10871364\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jeff_Niemann\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jeff_Niemann\"}, {\"begin\": 3520, \"end\": 3525, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/CJ_Perez\", \"score\": 0.9998942325591228, \"rank\": 8.616297284794906e-05, \"text\": \"Perez\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q3665646\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/CJ_Perez\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/CJ_Perez\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Day\", \"from\": 3485, \"to\": 3488}, {\"ngram\": \"Hojgaard\", \"from\": 3490, \"to\": 3498}, {\"ngram\": \"the outskirts\", \"from\": 3529, \"to\": 3542}, {\"ngram\": \"medal contention\", \"from\": 3546, \"to\": 3562}, {\"ngram\": \"a better stage\", \"from\": 3590, \"to\": 3604}, {\"ngram\": \"the game\", \"from\": 3617, \"to\": 3625}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Through nine holes, it appeared that Rahm, the two-time major champion who won last